headline: Citi shifts retail stock ratings
summary: Investing.com -- In separate notes Tuesday, analysts at Citi adjusted their ratings on two major retail stocks, Carter's Inc. (NYSE:CRI) and Ross Stores (NASDAQ:ROST), reflecting shifts in their respective business outlooks and potential challenges.
